data.description: Welcome to this stunning brick home that boasts 3400 square feet of living space on an acre lot in an beautiful, established neighborhood! The great room features a tall cathedral ceiling with exposed wood beams and a raised brick hearth. The chef kitchen is a dream come true with its wood floors, 6 burner gas cooktop, center island with prep sink, and double ovens. The breakfast room has a convenient wet bar. The master bedroom is located on the main floor for easy access and privacy, upstairs are an additional 3 bedrooms plus an oversized bonus room currently being used as a bedroom.  A delightful sunroom and a formal dining room complete this amazing home. Some TLC is needed to make it shine again. With an acceptable offer, the seller will include a 1-year home warranty not to exceed $600. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this your forever home!
